widgets_values:
The images created by IPAdapter are interrogated and the prompt is automatically created into a three part batch with proper syntax. Additionally, the batches are separated evenly into three parts based on the frame count chosen.

If you get an error on the batch prompt scheduler it might be because the prompt is too long. Try playing with the WD14 Tagger settings - that seems to help
